# <type>(<scope>): <subject>        # ≤100 chars, imperative ("add", not "added")
#
# <body: what changed and why; wrap at ~72 columns>
#
# <footer: BREAKING CHANGE: ... | Refs #issue>
#
# ── Types ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# feat     new analysis / chart / capability
# fix      bug fix
# docs     documentation only
# style    formatting, no code change
# refactor restructuring, no behavior change
# perf     performance
# test     tests
# build    dependencies / packaging
# ci       GitHub Actions / workflows
# chore    tooling, config, housekeeping
# revert   revert a previous commit
#
# Scopes (suggested): site utils etl data ci docs <race-name>
